formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction cost.

2.The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement, and applying an appropriate basis of preparation; and making estimates that are reasonable in the circumstances.

3.The certificate is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project solely for the purpose to enable comply with requirement of RERA , and should not be used by any other person or for any other purpose. Accordingly, we do not accept or assume any liability or any duty of care for any other purpose or to any other person to whom this certificate is shown or into whose hands it may come without our prior consent in writing.

4.The details mentioned in Annexure A such as carpet area, booking status, unit consideration, date of agreement to sale, encumbrance status, name, KYC and mobile numbers of allottees are as provided by the management. 

5.The promoter has converted unsecured loans into booking of residential/commercial units. The same has been confirmed with the management. Further we have relied upon the clarification given by the management with respect to the said matter. In case where the promoter has converted unsecured loans into booking we have given added 70% to clause 7 - "Amount withdrawn till date of this certificate as per the Books of Accounts and Bank Statement" in order to arrive at precise withdrawal limit.		
	
6.There are instances where unsecured loans have been deposited in collection account which is clarified by the management.
